subproject.description: The project aims at strengthening institutional capacity of the National Parliament between 2011 and beginning 2015. It focuses on four different but interrelated areas of support. The first one regards assistance to parliamentary administration. The second area is the one related to the support to legislators, national staff, civil servants and legal experts to perform their functions. Furthermore the project aims at enhancing the oversight capacity of the Parliament by improving internal capabilities. Finally, the project aims at strengthening inter-parliamentary relations with Portugese speaking countries and Pacific regiona countries.
